.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, garlic, raspberry, strawberry
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, software-developer, analyst, police-officer
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, guinea-pig, rat
1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating garlic##1
3. the owner of the dog is between the software-developer and the analyst##2
4. the analyst is between the owner of the dog and the person eating strawberry##2
5. the analyst is the owner of the rat##1
6. the nurse is the owner of the goat##1
7. the police-officer is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | strawberry  | raspberry | eggplant | garlic     |
| Job   | nurse | analyst   | police-officer  | software-developer    |
| Pet     | goat        | rat       | dog      | guinea-pig |

