.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, soy-milk, tea
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, kiwi, lime, orange
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, lily, iris, marigold
1. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lime is between the person drinking tea and the person who growsiris##2
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growslily##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
5. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating lime##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | coffee    | mirinda | tea           | soy-milk |
| Food       | artichoke | lime    | kiwi          | orange   |
| Flower      | iris  | lily   | marigold | bellflower  |

