.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk, tea
House: gothic-revival, victorian, art-deco, palace
4 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, horse, mouse
1. the art-deco house is the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the palace house is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the art-deco house and the gothic-revival house##2
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
6. the owner of the mouse is between the person drinking milk and the owner of the cat##2
7. the palace house is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | milk     | tea   |
| House   | gothic-revival | palace        | art-deco  | victorian  |
| Pet           | cat      | mouse         | hedgehog | horse |

