.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage, strawberry, watermelon
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, hamster, hedgehog
4 different games are played: monopoly, poker, domino, mah-jongg
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person playing poker is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the person eating strawberry is on the far right##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the owner of the cat is between the person eating watermelon and the person playing domino##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | watermelon | cabbage | asparagus | strawberry |
| Pet         | bird       | cat     | hamster   | hedgehog   |
| Game   | monopoly | poker | domino | mah-jongg |

 